column2: SELECT PA.ra, PA.dec, PA.l, PA.b, PA.g, PA.r, PA.u, (PA.g - PA.r - PA.extinction_g + PA.extinction_r) as gmr, (PA.u - PA.g - PA.extinction_u + PA.extinction_g) as umg into mydb.FirstQuadrant FROM PhotoObjAll PA WHERE PA.l < # PA.l > # PA.b < # PA.b > # PA.g < # (PA.u - PA.g - PA.extinction_u + PA.extinction_g) < # (PA.u - PA.g - PA.extinction_u + PA.extinction_g) > #
